items.name: SynapseX
items.description: Welcome to **Synapse X**, a powerful and versatile scripting engine designed for Roblox that empowers users to unlock the full potential of their gaming experience. With Synapse X, you can execute Lua scripts, customize gameplay, and enhance your overall interaction with Roblox.
